headline: PayPal Giving Fund Canada crosses $200M milestone benefitting charities across Canada
summary: PayPal Giving Fund Canada announced that it has surpassed the $200 million mark in donations to registered charities across Canada since its inception. This significant milestone highlights the power of online giving and its ability to drive positive social impact.
